    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: #ffffff; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12pt;\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">尊敬的商家：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt; text-indent: 20pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: #ffffff; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12pt;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">您好，为适应业务发展和满足商家经营需求，京东新增部分类目商品阈值，现修订</span></span><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1211622812805107712\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">《京东开放平台个人</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">/个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》</span></span></u></a><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2025年</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">月</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">21</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">- 2025年</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">月</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">27</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">日，规则预计于</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2025年</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">8</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt; text-indent: 20pt; padding: 0pt; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: #ffffff; font-family: 等线; font-size: 12pt;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #000000; font-size: 10.0000pt; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">具体新增和调整情况见下表。</span></span></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 336.52pt;\" border=\"0\" width=\"673\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 54.00pt;\" span=\"2\" width=\"108\" /> <col style=\"width: 120.00pt;\" width=\"240\" /> <col style=\"width: 108.50pt;\" width=\"217\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.50pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.5pt; width: 54pt; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; background: #c00000; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; font-style: normal; white-space: nowrap;\" width=\"108\" height=\"33\">变更类型</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54pt; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; background: #c00000; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; font-style: normal; white-space: nowrap;\" width=\"108\">一级类目</td>\n<td style=\"width: 120pt; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; background: #c00000; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; font-style: normal; white-space: nowrap;\" width=\"240\">二级类目</td>\n<td style=\"width: 108.5pt; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; background: #c00000; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; font-style: normal; white-space: nowrap;\" width=\"217\">类目阈值</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.50pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.5pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\" height=\"33\">新增</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">医药</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">儿科专科用药OTC</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">20</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.50pt;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.5pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\" height=\"33\">新增</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">美妆护肤</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">精油/芳疗</td>\n<td style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; border: 0.5pt solid #000000; text-align: center; padding-top: 1px; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: nowrap;\">50</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
